The Goodwater Approach

Our investment approach starts with Genesis, a program that provides resources and wisdom to an unprecedented population of seed-stage entrepreneurs. It grows through Capital, with powerful investments in consumer technology startups that are shaping global culture and transforming the global economy. And finally, the loop closes with Collective, reinvesting profits back into Goodwater portfolio companies to provide consumer technology services for those in need.

Genesis

Our Genesis program is built to democratize access to seed funding and entrepreneurial guidance, opening doors that have traditionally felt more like hurdles than opportunities. It equips founders everywhere with startup curriculum, data, software, insights, wisdom, and a curated community that allows entrepreneurs to learn from our deep experiences, and from one another.
